  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time incremental view maintenance using differential dataflow",
    "PostgreSQL wire protocol compatibility for standard SQL queries",
    "Native CDC connectors for PostgreSQL, MySQL, and SQL Server",
    "Kafka integration for streaming data ingestion and output",
    "Strong consistency guarantees across multiple data sources",
    "Horizontally scalable compute with cluster-based architecture",
    "Support for complex SQL including multi-way joins and aggregations",
    "SUBSCRIBE command for streaming query results"
  ],
